channel.title: I won 3rd place in the FBLA compitition and going to nationals! And I need help
channel.description:
I won 3rd place in a convention against many other students in "Intro to Technology Concepts."
[code]If yo do not care, do not post.[/code]
I am going to the national competition, in Chicago. However, I need you help(for people that use databases) I went with about 9 questions about a database that starts with h, has the letters: h, e, i, y, c. That is all I can remember, they had weird questions about it that I did not know the answers to, please help me.
